24:42.480 --> 24:43.815
The fuck?

24:55.118 --> 24:56.369
[toilet flushing]

25:21.603 --> 25:22.729
[swishing]

25:39.663 --> 25:42.165
-[door opens]
-[Jacob] All right.

25:42.916 --> 25:43.917
Sorry...

25:45.126 --> 25:46.836
it took me so long.

25:50.674 --> 25:51.675
Karen?

25:59.182 --> 26:00.183
Karen?

26:40.807 --> 26:44.269
I just can't fucking believe it!
All you did was hurt a person.

26:44.352 --> 26:47.647
That's all you did,
was hurt a person that was already hurt.

26:47.731 --> 26:48.732
Can we get Terry, please?

26:48.815 --> 26:51.568
You're a morally bankrupt fucking monster.

26:51.651 --> 26:52.694
-Okay.
-Publicist.

26:52.777 --> 26:54.529
What do you mean, "Okay," funny face?

26:54.612 --> 26:56.364
-I didn't make a funny face.
-Jesus. Fuck!

26:56.448 --> 26:59.576
Why did you do that?
Why would you fucking do that?

26:59.659 --> 27:03.038
I told you not to do that.
All you did was hurt somebody.

27:03.121 --> 27:05.123
-Terry's here.
-Okay, well... Terry, hi!

27:05.206 --> 27:07.125
-[Terry]  Jacob? Jacob, can you see--
-What?

27:07.208 --> 27:09.377
It's Terry. Jacob, how are you doing?

27:09.461 --> 27:11.880
You don't have to say your name
when you're on the fucking TV.

27:11.963 --> 27:15.675
Well, I can't see you, Jacob.
[stammers]  Can you sit down or something?

27:15.759 --> 27:18.636
-Terry, what the fuck-- What did you do?
-We see you.

27:18.720 --> 27:20.930
-What's the problem?
-These fucking animals,

27:21.014 --> 27:23.641
fucking monster
and her henchman doofus here,

27:23.725 --> 27:27.270
they took those pictures of me and Karen
arguing and put 'em out in the world.

27:27.354 --> 27:30.148
She took 'em behind my back
when I was just standing there.

27:30.231 --> 27:33.109
-I went there to make a point.
-My understanding was you were aware

27:33.193 --> 27:34.736
that the picture was gonna be posted.

27:34.819 --> 27:36.988
Who told you that?
Lying sack of shit here?

27:37.072 --> 27:40.241
On some level, there was knowledge
that something was being done.

27:40.325 --> 27:43.995
-Lauren is a very truthful person, Jacob.
-Wait, what?

27:44.079 --> 27:46.122
You can trust what Lauren tells you.

27:46.206 --> 27:47.290
Are you out of your mind?

27:47.374 --> 27:50.752
She's a publicist! There's no truth there!
It's like a void!

27:50.835 --> 27:52.587
-A moral void.
-Okay... I mean...

27:52.670 --> 27:56.091
[Terry]  She's only trying to do
what's best for the project, Jacob.

27:56.174 --> 27:58.510
I think you might like to know

27:58.593 --> 28:02.806
that pre-sales have gone up
probably 40, 50 times

28:02.889 --> 28:05.183
- [Lauren] Mmm!
-since that picture was posted.

28:05.266 --> 28:07.560
-All right, so, I guess--
-[Amanda]  They're in the top 10%!

28:07.644 --> 28:08.770
What?

28:08.853 --> 28:11.022
They're in the top 10% of sales right now.

28:11.106 --> 28:14.150
[Jacob] Oh, okay,
you guys are a great team.

28:14.234 --> 28:17.570
And the  New York Review of Books
is talking about doing an article.

28:17.654 --> 28:19.989
-All right.
-And the fans are loving it.

28:20.073 --> 28:21.950
-They are eating it all up.
-Of course.

28:22.033 --> 28:25.120
Lauren, did you tell him about Jimmy yet?

28:25.203 --> 28:27.372
-Oh! Oh...
-Jimmy. Who's Jimmy?

28:27.455 --> 28:29.499
"Who's Jimmy?" I don't know. Jimmy Fallon.

28:29.582 --> 28:30.792
-What about Jimmy Fallon?
-Yeah.

28:30.875 --> 28:32.335
-The Tonight Show?
-[Jacob] Uh-huh.

28:32.419 --> 28:35.547
Would you like to be a guest,
do the couch with Jimmy?

28:36.881 --> 28:38.633
-[stammers]
-Yeah, yeah, got it.

28:38.717 --> 28:40.051
-Oh, yeah?
-I got you on. Yeah.

28:40.135 --> 28:42.137
-All right, well, that's--
-[Terry]  On the couch.

28:42.220 --> 28:44.723
On the couch, honey, the couch.

28:44.806 --> 28:46.516
That shirt really brings out your eyes.

28:46.599 --> 28:49.269
Okay! Okay. Can I just say one thing?

28:49.352 --> 28:52.230
I just wanna point out
that this doesn't make it right.

28:52.313 --> 28:55.984
You all hurt someone's feelings.
You're craven. You're all fucking craven.

28:56.067 --> 28:57.152
You too, Terry!

28:57.235 --> 28:59.362
And you too, Himmler. All right?

29:00.071 --> 29:03.700
All right. That said,
did anyone talk to Colbert?

29:03.783 --> 29:06.035
Did anyone reach out to Colbert? Anybody?

